    usf:disclaims ncl:bootstrapmarkernotreadiness , ncl:canonicaldomainmarkeronly , ncl:controlmappingnotoperatingeffectiveness , ncl:deferredcapabilities , ncl:draftsoanotapproved , ncl:inmemorynotservicebacked , ncl:lineagenotcurrentreadiness , ncl:noaccessibilitycompliance , ncl:nocertification , ncl:nohumanacceptance , ncl:nolaunchi18n , ncl:noliveproviderreadiness , ncl:nomonetisationconsentprovider , ncl:nootelcompliance , ncl:noproductionreadiness , ncl:nostorecdndeployment , ncl:nouiproductparity , ncl:productionshapednotproductionlive , ncl:reportslowestauthority .
